OL,3,CAirport planning 'further expansion'
OL,4,Cto exceed 12m passengers a year
OL,6,FBristol Airport's chief executive has
OL,7,Frevealed that further expansion plans
OL,8,Fcould be on the horizon.
OL,10,FDave Lees, CEO, has exclusively told
OL,11,FITV News West Country that demand to
OL,12,Fexceed the existing limit of 12
OL,13,Fmillion passengers a year is growing.
OL,15,FThe airport is already expanding, with
OL,16,Fwork underway on a second four-level
OL,17,Fcar park for 2,000 vehicles, as well
OL,18,Fas expanded bus and coach parking with
OL,19,Fa new drop-off and pick-up area.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
