OL,3,CAirport planning 'further expansion'
OL,4,Cto exceed 12m passengers a year
OL,6,FMr Lees said: "We'll come forward in a
OL,7,Ftimely manner and consult with people,
OL,8,Fof course, taking views from people as
OL,9,Fwe look to fulfil the demand from
OL,10,Fpassengers in the future.
OL,12,F"We constantly look at trends in air
OL,13,Ftravel and what we've been really
OL,14,Fpleasantly surprised by is that people
OL,15,Freally do want to continue to travel.
