OL,4,Cto exceed 12m passengers a year
OL,6,F"We've seen since the pandemic a real
OL,7,Fresurgence in terms of people wanting
OL,8,Fto connect with friends and family
OL,9,Facross Europe as well as across the
OL,10,Fworld and that will inform our plans
OL,11,Fas we go forward over the coming
OL,12,Fyears."
