OL,3,CAirport planning 'further expansion'
OL,4,Cto exceed 12m passengers a year
OL,6,FCommenting on congestion on the A38
OL,7,Fthat borders the airport, Mr Lees
OL,8,Fadded: "We work very closely with
OL,9,FNorth Somerset (Council) as well as he
OL,10,Fcombined authority looking to see how
OL,11,Froad improvements can be brought
OL,12,Fforward and the A38 has schemes coming
OL,13,Fforward complementing the work we're
OL,14,Ftaking place to enhance the
OL,15,Faccessibility to the airport."
