OL,3,CAirport planning 'further expansion'
OL,4,Cto exceed 12m passengers a year
OL,6,FMore than 100,000 tons of materials
OL,7,Fare being reused on a site which is
OL,8,Fbeing transformed and will be
OL,9,Fsurrounded by a new road network. The
OL,10,Ffirst contractors have been preparing
OL,11,Ffoundations for about a year and now
OL,12,Fmore than 100 are on site.
OL,14,FRichard Tidmarsh, Infrastructure
OL,15,FDirector of contractors Griffiths
OL,16,Fsaid: "This is part of the reason why
OL,17,FI went into civil engineering. I've
OL,18,Fbeen in the industry for 28 years and
OL,19,Fyou go to a lot of places and it makes
OL,20,Fyou proud to feel a part of something
OL,21,Fthat's making a difference."
