OL,3,CAirport planning 'further expansion'
OL,4,Cto exceed 12m passengers a year
OL,6,FA public consultation is imminent,
OL,7,Fwith a detailed planning application
OL,8,Fdue early next year.
OL,10,FIt's a move opponents, including
OL,11,Fvillagers near the site, may dread but
OL,12,Fairport bosses say expansion will be
OL,13,Fled by market forces and planning
OL,14,Fapproval while supporting new
OL,15,Ftechnologies, like quieter aircraft,
OL,16,Fto mitigate its impact.
OL,18,FBristol is the UK's largest regional
OL,19,Fairport without a rail link, and so
OL,20,Fthere will be fears expansion could
OL,21,Fadd to congestion on the A38.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
