OL,3,CAirport planning 'further expansion'
OL,4,Cto exceed 12m passengers a year
OL,6,FThis means greater public transport
OL,7,Fprovision is vital if the site is to
OL,8,Fhit its target of becoming a carbon
OL,9,Fneutral ground operation by 2030.
OL,11,FAlthough bus and coach use has more
OL,12,Fthan doubled in the last year, it
OL,13,Fstill only accounts for 16% of
OL,14,Fjourneys, making another car park
OL,15,Ftempting in practical and financial
OL,16,Fterms.
